    "To validate the robustness of the BiLLP framework across various base models, we conduct additional experiments with other different LLM backbones: \"gpt-4-32k\" and \"Llama-2-7b\".",
    "The results are presented in Table 6.From the table, several noteworthy observations can be made:• BiLLP showcases superior performance compared to traditional RL-based methods with different base models, as demonstrated in Table 6.",
    "This indicates that our framework is robust across different LLMs.",
    "• The performance of BiLLP based on \"GPT-3.5-16k\" is superior to that based on \"Llama-2-7B\", while inferior to that based on \"GPT-4-32k\".",
